      {
        "scenario": "OrderService succeeds but PaymentService fails — orphaned order with reserved stock",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "Implement a compensation/saga pattern: on PaymentService failure, CartService must call OrderService to cancel the order and release reserved inventory. Alternatively, switch to a reservation-with-expiry model where uncommitted reservations auto-expire."
