        "scenario": "OrderService sustained degradation — no circuit breaker protection",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "Add a circuit breaker on CartService→OrderService, similar to the PaymentService circuit breaker. Without it, OrderService degradation will cascade into CartService thread exhaustion."
      },
