        "scenario": "External payment gateway sustained outage — no circuit breaker",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "Add a circuit breaker on PaymentService→Gateway. Without it, all PaymentService threads block for 8s each, exhausting the service and cascading back through CartService to users."
